5 We always enjoy Tavern Grille.   The menu has a wide variety of food.  We have tried many of the items and have never been disappointed.  They grind their hamburger in house and they are always great.   I always ask for well done for hamburgers,  and they always are cooked that way.  Also, they come out juicy ...which some places don't know how to do.   They have food specials daily,  all of which are great.   Although this is classified as a bar, they are family friendly.  We don't do alcohol but we are never hassled about drinks.  At least one of the owners is always here and that makes a difference.   Staff is very friendly.   Don't miss this place!
